(94071, 24433, 0, 1, '在天堂的另一邊(acoustic demo)', 'Acoustic Demo Version\n\n詞/曲 - Tyler/Vank\n編曲 - NeverMind\n\nFacebook Fanpage: https://www.facebook.com/NeverMind.JustNeverMind', '2013-01-01 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 0, 5, '你心中的角落，還在守候，那微微閃爍的燈火。\n無須解釋理由，不想多說，無怨無悔為愛等候。\n冷眼的看透，這瘋狂世界無對錯。\n伴隨著節奏，踏著舞步朝向墜落。\n\n舞台上的樂手，狂野嘶吼，上演著激情的獨奏。\n慾望宣洩奔流，盡情放縱，仿如小說某個段落。\n隨風似漂流，昨是今非已不相同。\n燦爛的瞬間，轉身錯過不能回頭。\n\n凌晨三點鐘，漫長的黑夜最深沉最朦朧，\n你是否後悔過？堅持守候愛人曾經美麗的臉孔？\n淚與夜交錯，孤寂的靈魂最黑暗最懦弱。\n曾擁有失去過，仍然微笑面對終要毀滅的自我？\n\n在最後的最後，終於放手。\n曲終人散僅剩落寞。\n喝完這一杯酒，不再疑惑，故事終究會有盡頭。\n想留住什麼，但雙手已無法緊握。\n這一絲笑容，是你遺留下的往後。\n\n凌晨三點鐘，漫長的黑夜最深沉最朦朧，\n你是否後悔過？堅持守候愛人曾經美麗的臉孔？\n淚與夜交錯，孤寂的靈魂最黑暗最懦弱。\n曾擁有失去過，仍然微笑面對終要毀滅的自我？\n', '', 336, '', 'Vank', 'Tyler', 'NeverMind', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2015-01-11 13:53:09', '2015-03-12 14:17:59', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(94072, 331744, 0, 1, 'Illusions', '自由', '2015-02-14 00:00:00', 2000, 19, 1, 9, 'There can be no future where I will be defeated by\nthose who lie and say that we are free.\n\n\nTheir chains are moving closer, the shields are fading, our blood is thickening the air.\nBurn these towers that cage our desires, we won''t be slaves for what''s rightfully ours.\n\nHear them calling. \nScreaming and begging for help.\nThe sight of hope is fading.\n\nSo take up arms, and burn these walls, if freedom speaks it speaks through war.\n\nEmbrace the bloodshed and screams of despair, this is the price that freedom bears.\nThere is no other way, fight to be saved.\nCleanse these streets with blood, blood of the tyrants.\n\nDon''t tell yourself that it''s fine no it isn''t,\nYou think you''re free but they told you what it means\n\nDon''t tell yourself that it''s fine no it isn''t,\nYou think you''re free but they told you what it means\n\n\nDon''t tell yourself that it''s fine no it isn''t,\nYou think you''re free but they taught you what that word means \nIt''s not as it seems\n\n\nHear them calling. \nEndlessly fading.\n\nHear them calling.\nOver and over and over again.\nThe sight of hope is fading.\n\nSo take up arms, and burn these walls, if freedom speaks it speaks through war.', '', 236, '', 'Parallel Horizons', 'Naseem', 'Wilfred Ho', 'Parallel Horizons', '', 0, 1, 0, '2015-01-11 13:57:18', '2015-03-12 14:17:59', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(94073, 331744, 0, 1, 'Asphyxia', '這是一首關於失戀的歌.', '2015-02-14 00:00:00', 2000, 19, 1, 9, 'Everyone is watching.\nAs I threw her into the lions'' den.\nTo be ripped apart\nlike she did my heart.\n\nThe wicked must be punished.\nShe said sorry!!\n\nBroken she is begging\nMy eyes they lust for red\n\nYou can crawl, you can scream, but remember \nthat these hands will never stop until your face has turned to nothing. \n\nA bitch until the end.\n\nFather, holy father, \nIs this a sin?\nAll I want is to punish this evil bitch.\n\nEveryone was watching.\nAs she begged for mercy.\n\nSleep, broken one, eternally, in agony.\nSeek solace, but there will be none for thee.\nScream and struggle, endlessly suffer.\nSleep, my angel, in silence, forever.\n', '', 220, '', 'Parallel Horizons', 'Naseem', 'Wilfred Ho', 'Parallel Horizons', '', 0, 1, 0, '2015-01-11 13:57:43', '2015-03-12 14:17:59', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(94074, 24433, 0, 1, '不晟子 - 2015/01/03 Live Version', '現場演出側錄-2015/01/03 @ 板橋飛音樂展演空間\n\n詞/曲-Vank\n編曲-NeverMind\n\nFacebook Fanpage: https://www.facebook.com/NeverMind.JustNeverMind', '2013-01-01 00:00:00', 2000, 19, 1, 1, '阮是阮叨厝內ㄟ一咧不晟子\n年過三十也袂討一咧媳婦仔\n也沒賺到一筆乎阮變好野人\n聽嘸恁ㄟ苦勸 猶原一天過一天\n\n原諒阮這幾年攏係咧跑外口\n袂當帶身軀邊照顧恁ㄟ生活\n目周金金看恁年歲越來越大\n每日辛苦打拼 操煩嘎留白頭鬃\n\n阮嘸係求名聲\n只是看嘸自己的形影\n請體諒 阮心情\n未來有風有雨我知道\n感謝恁 無怨言\n聲聲對阮講要有信心\n這句話 阮會記得\n春暖花開阮叨來轉去\n\n阮是阮叨厝內ㄟ一咧不晟子\n時間緊緊風靜靜擱要過一冬\n乎阮心內漸漸ㄟ感覺到驚惶\n就算孤單作伴 阮要繼續阮的夢', '', 242, '', 'Vank', 'Vank', 'NeverMind', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2015-01-11 14:35:10', '2015-03-12 14:17:59', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
